 text.'=>'Gehitu saski testura.','Add to cart description.'=>'Gehitu saski deskripziora.','Add to cart details.'=>'Gehitu saski xehetasunetara.','Sorry, you cannot update resources.'=>'Barkatu, ezin dituzu balioabideak eguneratu.','The entity type must be "order".'=>'Entitate mota "eskaria" izan behar da.','The entity ID is required.'=>'Entitate identifikatzailea beharrezkoa da.','The order ID is required.'=>'Eskari identifatzailea beharrezkoa da.','Sorry, you are not allowed to perform this action.'=>'Barkatu, ez daukazu ekintza hau burutzeko baimenik.','Expected an array of country codes.'=>'Herrialde kode matriza espero da.','When enabled, PayPal will use the address provided by the checkout form, and prevent the buyer from changing it inside the PayPal payment page. Disable this to let buyers choose a shipping address from their PayPal account. PayPal verifies addresses therefore this setting can cause errors (we recommend keeping it disabled).'=>'Gaituta dagoenean, ordainketa formularioan emandako helbidea erabiliko du PayPalek, eta bezeroak PayPal ordainketa orrian aldatzea eragotziko du. Desgaitu hau bezeroari bere PayPal kontutik bidalketa helbidea aukeratzen uzteko. PayPalek helbideak egiaztatzen ditu eta ondorioz ezarpen honek erroreak eragin ditzake (desgaituta mantentzea gomendatzen dugu).','"Reply-to" name'=>'"Erantzun-honi" izena','"Reply-to" address'=>'"Erantzun-honi" helbidea','Prevent buyers from changing the shipping address.'=>'Bezeroak bidalketa helbidea aldatzea ekiditen du.','Payment pending (reason: %s).'=>'Ordainketaren zain (zergaitia: %s).','Enable PayPal buttons to offer PayPal, Venmo and Pay Later as express checkout options on product, cart, and checkout pages.'=>'Gaitu PayPal botoia, produktu, saski eta ordainketa orrietan, PayPal, Venmo eta Pay Later erosketa azkar aukeretan eskaintzeko.','Enable PayPal Buttons'=>'Gaitu PayPal Botoiak','PayPal Buttons'=>'PayPal Botoiak','PayPal payment authorized. Transaction ID: %1$s. Change payment status to processing or complete to capture funds.'=>'PayPal ordainketa onartuta. Transakzio IDa: %1$s. Aldatu ordainketa prozesatzen edo osatuta egoerara funtsak jasotzeko.','PayPal payment captured. Transaction ID: %1$s.'=>'PayPal ordainketa harrapatuta. Transakzio IDa: %1$s.','PayPal payment approval failed. PayPal Order ID: %1$s. Status: %2$s'=>'PayPal ordainketa onarpenak huts egin du. PayPal Eskari IDa: %1$s. Egoera: %2$s','PayPal payment approved. PayPal Order ID: %1$s'=>'PayPal ordainketa onartzeak huts egin du. PayPal Eskari IDa: %1$s','PayPal capture authorized payment failed'=>'PayPal ordainketa autorizazio harrapatzeak huts egin du','. PayPal debug ID: %s'=>'. PayPal arazketa IDa: %s','PayPal %1$s payment failed. PayPal Order ID: %2$s'=>'PayPal %1$s ordainketak huts egin du. PayPal Eskari IDa: %2$s','PayPal order creation failed. PayPal debug ID: %1$s'=>'PayPal eskari sortzeak huts egin du. PayPal arazketa IDa: %1$s','WooCommerce has upgraded your PayPal integration from PayPal Standard to PayPal Payments (PPCP), for a more reliable and modern checkout experience. If you do not prefer the upgraded integration in WooCommerce, we recommend switching to %1$sPayPal Payments%2$s extension.'=>'WooCommercek zure PayPal integrazioa PayPal Standardetik PayPal Paymentsera (PPCP) bertsio-berritu du, erosketa prozesu sinesgarri eta modernoago baterako. Ez baduzu bertsio-berritutako WooCommerce integrazioa nahi, %1$sPaypal Payments%2$s hedapenera aldatzea gomendatzen dizugu.','An unknown error occurred'=>'Errore ezezaguna gertatu da','We are unable to process your PayPal payment at this time. Please try again or use a different payment method.'=>'Ezin izan dugu zure PayPal ordainketa prozesatu une honetan. Saiatu berriro mesedez edo erabili beste ordainketa modu bat.','Requires a plugin with predictive address search support (e.g. <a href="%s" target="_blank">WooPayments</a>).'=>'Helbide bilaketa prediktiboa daukan plugina behar du (adb. <a href="%s" target="_blank">WooPayments</a>).','Enable taxes and coupons and configure how they are calculated.'=>'Gaitu zergak eta kupoiak eta konfiguratu nola kalkulatzen diren.','Taxes and coupons'=>'Zergak eta kupoiak','Dādra and Nagar Haveli and Damān and Diu'=>'Dādra eta Nagar Haveli eta Damān eta Diu','Kosovo'=>'Kosobo','block titleStatus Filter'=>'Egoera Iragazkia','block titleActive Filters'=>'Gaitutako Iragazkiak','block titleAttribute Filter'=>'Atributu Iragazkia','block titlePrice Filter'=>'Prezioa Iragazkia','block descriptionA placeholder block for email content.'=>'E-posta edukiarentzat leku-marka blokea.','block titleEmail Content'=>'E-posta Edukia','Full screen image'=>'Pantaila osoko irudia','Notify me'=>'Jakinarazi ni','back in stock formEnter your e-mail'=>'Sartu zure e-posta','Want to be notified when this product is back in stock?'=>'Nahi duzu abisatzea produktu hau berriro eskuragarri dagoenean?','back in stock formEmail address to be notified when this product is back in stock'=>'Produktua berriro eskuragarri dagoela abisatzeko e-posta helbidea','You have received this message because your e-mail address was used to sign up for stock notifications on our store. Wasn\'t you? Please get in touch with us if you keep receiving these messages.'=>'Mezu hau jaso duzu zure e-posta helbidea eskuragarritasun abisuetan altan eman delako gure dendan. Ez zara zu izan? Mesedez, jarri harremanetan gurekin mezu hauek jasotzen jarraitu nahiko bazenu.','To stop receiving these messages, %s to unsubscribe.'=>'Mezu hauek jasotzeari uzteko, harpidetza uzteko %s.','This link will remain active for %s.'=>'Esteka hau %s aktibo egongo da.','unsubscribe cta for stock notifications for existing customersclick here'=>'klikatu hemen','unsubscribe cta for stock notifications for guestsclick here'=>'klikatu hemen','To manage your notifications, %s to log in to your account.'=>'Zure jakinarazpenak kudeatzeko, zure kontuan saioa hasteko %s.','You have received this message because your e-mail 