ult shipping partner suggestions when woocommerce_show_marketplace_suggestions option is set to no'=>'Itzuli bidalketako bazkidearen iradokizunak woocommerce_show_marketplace_suggestions aukera ezezkoan dagoenean.','Array of transaction processors and their images.'=>'Transakzio-prozesadoreen eta haien irudien matrizea.','placeholder for search fieldSearch products…'=>'Bilatu produktuak...','Message explaining that there are no products returned from a searchNo products were found matching your selection.'=>'Zure aukerekin bat egiten duen produkturik ez da aurkitu.','Basic details'=>'Oinarrizko xehetasunak','Coupon removed: "%s".'=>'Kupoia kendu da: "%s".','Stock management'=>'Stock kudeaketa','Disabled in <a href="%s" aria-label="stock management store settings">store settings</a>.'=>'Desgaitu egin da <a href="%s" aria-label="stock management store settings">dendaren ezarpenetan</a>.','Stock management disabled in store settings'=>'Stockaren kudeaketa desgaitu egin da dendaren ezarpenetan','Track stock quantity for this product'=>'Jarraitu produktu honen stock kopurua','Settings below apply to all variations without manual stock management enabled. '=>'Stockaren eskuzko kudeaketa gaitu gabe duten produktu-aldaera guztiei aplikatzen zaizkie doikuntza hauek. ','Enter options for customers to choose from, f.e. “Blue” or “Large”. Use “%s” to separate different options.'=>'Sartu aukerak bezeroek hauta dezaten, adib. “Urdina” edo “Haundia”. Erabili "%s" aukera desberdinak bereizteko.','Autodetect'=>'Autodetektatu','Character encoding of the file'=>'Fitxategiaren karaktere-kodeketa','Make sure you enter the name and values for each attribute.'=>'Ziurtatu atributu bakoitzaren izena eta balioak sartzen dituzula.','block descriptionDisplay shopper-facing notifications generated by WooCommerce or extensions.'=>'Erakutsi WooCommerce-k edo luzapenek sortutako erosleei zuzendutako jakinarazpenak.','block titleStore Notices'=>'Dendako Oharrak','block descriptionDisplay the n