 ematen die, beti interesik gabe.','Afterpay'=>'Afterpay','You added store details'=>'Denda xehetasunak gehitu dituzu','You created %s'=>'%s sortu duzu','Get your products in front of Pinterest users searching for ideas and things to buy. Get started with Pinterest and make your entire product catalog browsable.'=>'Jarri zure produktuak Pinterest erabiltzaileen aurrean ideiak eta erosketak bilatzen ari direnean. Hasi Pinterest erabiltzen eta bihurtu zure produktuen katalogo osoa arakagarri.','Gateway title.'=>'Pasabidearen izenburua','Priority of recommendation.'=>'Gomendioaren lehentasuna','Array of plugin slugs.'=>'Plugin slug-en matrizea.','Suggestion visibility.'=>'Gomendioaren ikusgaitasuna.','Gateway image.'=>'Pasabidearen irudia.','Suggestion ID.'=>'Gomendioaren identifikatzailea.','Suggestion description.'=>'Gomendioaren deskripzioa.','Sorry, experiment_name is required.'=>'Barkatu, experiment_name beharrezkoa da.','Only show meta which is meant to be displayed for an order.'=>'Eskarian bistaratzeko den meta bakarrik erakutsi.','The downloadable file %s cannot be used as it has been disabled.'=>'%s fitxategi deskargagarria ezin da erabili desgaitu egin delako.','Headers already sent when generating download error message.'=>'Goiburuak aurretiaz bidali dira deskarga errore mezua sortzean.','The %1$sApproved Product Download Directories list%2$s has been updated. To protect your site, please review the list and make any changes that might be required. For more information, please refer to %3$sthis guide%2$s.'=>'%1$sOnartutako Produktu Deskarga Karpeten zerrenda%2$s eguneratu da. Zure gunea babesteko, mesedez, berrikusi zerrenda eta egin beharrezkoa ikustent duzun edozein aldaketa. Informazio gehiagorako, mesedez, ikusi %3$sgida hau%2$s.','Is your site enforcing the use of Approved Product Download Directories?'=>'Zure gunea Onartutako Produktu Deskargagarrien Karpeten erabilera betearazten ari da?','Enforce Approved Product Download Directories'=>'Betearazi Onartutako Produktu Deskargagarrien Karpetak','The indicated downloads have been disabled (invalid location or filetype&mdash;%1$slearn more%2$s).'=>'Zehaztuttako deskargak desgaitu dira (kokaleku edo fitxategi mota baliogabea&mdas;%1$sikasi gehiago%2$s).','Are you sure you wish to delete this item?'=>'Ziur al zaude elementu hau ezabatu nahi duzula?','Error saving order ID %1$s.'=>'%1$s ID eskaria gordetzean errorea.','(no ID)'=>'(IDrik ez)','Eswatini'=>'Eswatini','How easy was it to edit your product?'=>'Zein erraza izan da zure produktua editatzea?','Start shopping'=>'Erosten hasi','block descriptionBlock that displays the shopping button when the Mini-Cart is empty.'=>'Saski-Txikia hutsik dagoenean erosketa botoia bistaratzen duen blokea.','block titleMini-Cart Shopping Button'=>'Saski-Txiki Erosketa Botoia','Custom orders tables have been deleted.'=>'Eskarien taula pertsonalizatua ezabatu da.','Delete the custom orders tables'=>'Ezabatu eskarien taula pertsonalizatua','Nonce is invalid.'=>'Nonce baliogabea da.','Missing the Nonce header. This endpoint requires a valid nonce.'=>'Nonce goiburua falta da. Amaiera-puntu honek nonce balio egoki bat beharrezkoa du.','Plugin activation has been scheduled.'=>'Plugin gaitzea programatu da.','Plugin installation has been scheduled.'=>'Plugin instalazioa programatu da.','Optional parameter to get only specific task lists by id.'=>'Hautazko parametroa identifikatzailearen arabera ataza zerrenda jakinak eskuratzeko.','Shows if the product needs to be configured before it can be bought.'=>'Produktua erosi aurretik konfiguratu behar bada erakusten da.','Order payment URL.'=>'Eskari ordainketa URLa.','The maximum quantity that can be added to the cart.'=>'Saskira gehitu daitekeen gehienezko kopurua.','The minimum quantity that can be added to the cart.'=>'Saskira gehitu daitekeen gutxienezko kopurua.','Received PDT notification for another account: %1$s. Order ID: %2$d.'=>'PDT jakinarazpena jaso da beste kontu batentzat: %1$s. Eskari IDa: %2$d.','Received PDT notification for order %1$d on endpoint for order %2$d.'=>'PDT jakinarazpena jaso da %1$d eskariarentzat %2$d eskariaren amaiera puntuan.','block keywordWooCommerce'=>'WooCommerce','block titleCheckout'=>'Erosketa burutu','block descriptionDisplay a checkout form so your customers can submit orders.'=>'Bistaratu zure bezeroek eskariak egin ahal izateko ordainketa inprimakia.','block descriptionContains the products table and other custom blocks of filled mini-cart.'=>'Produktu taula eta osatutako saski-txikiaren beste bloke pertsonalizatuak hartzen ditu barne.','block titleMini-Cart Items'=>'Saski-Txiki Elementuak','Email address (optional)'=>'E-posta helbidea (hautazkoa)','This means that the table is probably in an inconsistent state. It\'s recommended to run a new regeneration process or to resume the aborted process (Status - Tools - Regenerate the product attributes lookup table/Resume the product attributes lookup table regeneration) before enabling the table usage.'=>'Horrek esan nahi du taula egoera inkoherente batean dagoela ziurrenik. Gomendagarria da birsorkuntza prozesu berri bat exekutatzea edo bertan behera utzitako prozesua berrabiaraztea (Egoera - Tresnak - Produktuaren atributuen bilaketa taula birsortu/Produktuaren atributuen bilaketa taularen birsorkuntza berrabiarazi) taularen erabilera gaitu aurretik.','Resume'=>'Jarraitu','WARNING: The product attributes lookup table regeneration process was aborted.'=>'KONTUZ: Produktuaren atributuen bilaketa taularen birsortzea utzi egin da.','Product attributes lookup table regeneration process has been resumed.'=>'Produktuaren atributuen bilaketa taularen birsortzea berrabiarazi da.','This tool will resume the product attributes lookup table regeneration at the point in which it was aborted (%1$s products were already processed).'=>'Tresna honek produktuen atributuen bilaketa taularen birsortzea berrabiaraziko du utzi zen puntu berean (%1$s produktu aurretiaz prozesatuta).','Resume the product attributes lookup table regeneration'=>'Berrabiarazi produktuen atributuen bilaketa taularen birsortzea','Product attributes lookup table regeneration process has been aborted.'=>'Produktuen atributuen bilaketa taularen birsortzea bertan behera utzi da.','This tool will abort the regenerate product attributes lookup table regeneration. After this is done the process can be either started over, or resumed to continue where it stopped.'=>'Tresna honek produktuen atributuen bilaketa taularen birsortzea utziko du. Hau eginda dagoenean prozesua berriro hasi daiteke hasieratik edo utzitako lekutik.','Abort the product attributes lookup table regeneration'=>'Utzi produktuen atributuen bilaketa taularen birsortzea','The amount that quantities increment by. Quantity must be an multiple of this value.'=>'Kantitatea zenbatean handituko den adierazten duen kopurua. Kantitatea balio honen multiploa izan behar da.','How the quantity of this item should be controlled, for example, any limits in place.'=>'Ea elementu honen kantitatea nola kontroaltu behar den, adibidez, ezarritako mugak.','Quantity of this item to add to the cart.'=>'Saskira gehitzeko elementu honen kantitatea.','Changing platforms might seem like a big hurdle to overcome, but it is easier than you might think to move your products, customers, and orders to WooCommerce. This article will help you with going through this process.'=>'Plataforma aldatzeak, gainditzeko oztopo handia dirudien arren, uste baino errazagoa da zure produktuak, bezeroak eta eskaerak WooCommerce-ra eramatea. Artikulu honek prozesu horretan lagunduko dizu.','Berlin'=>'Berlin','How to Migrate from Magento to WooCommerce'=>'Nola migratu Magento-tik WooCommerce-ra','Thuringia'=>'Thuringia','Schleswig-Holstein'=>'Schleswig-Holstein','Saxony-Anhalt'=>'Saxony-Anhalt','Saxony'=>'Saxony','Saarland'=>'Saarland','Rhineland-Palatinate'=>'Rhineland-Palatinate','North Rhine-Westphalia'=>'North Rhine-Westphalia','Lower Saxony'=>'Low