.'=>'%s ezin dira erosi. Mesedez, kendu itzazu zure saskitik.','%s are out of stock and cannot be purchased. Please remove them from your cart.'=>'%s stock gabe daude eta ezin dira erosi. Mesedez, kendu itzazu zure saskitik.','%s is out of stock and cannot be purchased. Please remove it from your cart.'=>'%s stock gabe dago eta ezin da erosi. Mesedez, kendu zure saskitik.','Step'=>'pausu','Tax class slug is invalid'=>'Zerga klase slug-a baliogabea da','City name, it doesn\'t support multiple values. Deprecated as of WooCommerce 5.3, \'cities\' should be used instead.'=>'Hiri izena, ez ditu balio bat baino gehiago onartzen. WooCommerce 5.3 bertsiotik aurrera zaharkituta, \'cities\' erabili beharko litzateke.','Postcode/ZIP, it doesn\'t support multiple values. Deprecated as of WooCommerce 5.3, \'postcodes\' should be used instead.'=>'Posta kodea/ZIP, ez ditu balio anitz onartzen. WooCommerce 5.3 bertsiotik aurrera zaharkituta, \'posta kodeak\' erabili beharko lirateke.','List of city names. Introduced in WooCommerce 5.3.'=>'Hiri izenen zerrenda. WooCommerce 5.3an gehitua.','List of postcodes / ZIPs. Introduced in WooCommerce 5.3.'=>'Posta kode / ZIP zerrenda. WooCommerce 5.3an gehitua.','Amount that will be refunded for this tax.'=>'Zerga honentzat itzuliko den kopurua.','Amount that will be refunded for this line item (excluding taxes).'=>'Elementu lerro honentzat itzuliko den kopurua (zergak kanpo utzita).','Low Stock amount for the variation.'=>'Stock Baxu kopurua aldaerarentzat.','Limit result set to resources assigned to a specific parent. Applies to hierarchical taxonomies only.'=>'Mugatu emaitzak zehaztutako gurasoa zehaztuta duten baliabideetara. Taxonomia hierarkikoei soilik aplikatzen zaie.','Offset the result set by a specific number of items. Applies to hierarchical taxonomies only.'=>'Emaitza multzoan elementu kopuru jakin bat kanpoan utzi. Taxonomia hierarkikoetan bakarrik aplikatzen da.','Low Stock amount for the product.'=>'Stock Baxu kopurua produktu